    @CreoleResource(name="GATE .cochrane.txt document format",
                comment="<html>Load this to allow the opening of Cochrane text documents, and choose the mime type <strong>\"text/x-cochrane\"</strong>, or use the correct file extension.",
                autoinstances=,
                isPrivate=true)
public class CochraneTextDocumentFormat
extends PubmedTextDocumentFormat
    A document format analyser for Cochrane text documents. Use mime type value "text/x-cochrane", or file extension ".cochrane.txt" to access this document format.
